headline: Trane Technologies and Autodesk Collaborate to Accelerate and Simplify Sustainable Building Design
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, November 12, 2024--Trane Technologies (NYSE:TT), a global climate innovator and Autodesk, Inc. (NASDAQ: ADSK), a global leader in building information modeling (BIM) technology for the architecture, engineering, construction (AEC) and operations industry, announced a strategic collaboration aimed at optimizing commercial building design for sustainability.
